    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "さて。ドラマの台本も届いたことだし\n約束通り、君には演技の練習に付き合ってもらうからね",
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや……練習に付き合うのはやぶさかじゃないけど\n俺はマネージャーであって、演技のプロじゃないぞ",
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子あたりは、演技でもわりと評価されてるし\n頼めば手伝ってくれるだろうけど……",
      "startTime": 21.096417141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "せめて男相手じゃないと、感覚がまるで掴めないからね\nそうなると、身近な男なんて君くらいしかいないだろ",
      "startTime": 28.5297504743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ただでさえ、恋愛なんてさっぱりなんだから\n練習はしっかりやっておかないと",
      "startTime": 37.0964204471,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11003.5795529,
          "startTime": 48.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか\nええと……それじゃあ、最初のシーンから……",
      "startTime": 41.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "病める時も、健やかなる時も、富める時も、貧しき時も\n妻として愛し、敬い、慈しむことを誓いますか？",
      "startTime": 58.3333366394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "はい",
      "startTime": 64.3394365629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……そこ、もうちょっと嬉しそうな方が良くないか？",
      "startTime": 65.9727678617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "これでも感極まった感を出したつもりだったんだけど\n……じゃあ、次の台詞",
      "startTime": 75.5925407411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに祝福されて、あなたと結ばれるなんて\n思ってもみなかったから……今でも、なんだか夢みたい",
      "startTime": 81.692536672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もう絶対に、君を手放したりなんかするものか\nずっと、君を幸せにする……する、から……",
      "startTime": 93.2666669208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "練習なんだから、ちゃんとやってくれなきゃ困るよ\n大人なんだし、結婚式に出た経験くらいないの？",
      "startTime": 104.9676807403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、親戚の結婚式に出たことはあるけど……\nでも見てるだけと自分でやるのとは、全然違うだろう！",
      "startTime": 112.1666531878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうか\n見ただけで真似出来るなら、僕だって苦労はしてないし",
      "startTime": 117.9988301595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "付き合うとか、結婚するとか……\n台本があっても、やっぱり全然想像出来ないや",
      "startTime": 125.8988291423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……\n花婿の台詞なら、ちょっと出来る気がするんだけどな",
      "startTime": 132.3988423665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "もう絶対に、君を手放したりなんかするものか\n一生、君を幸せにするから、そばにいてくれないか",
      "startTime": 142.7321807861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい",
      "startTime": 148.6321726481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "おお。今の君の反応は、ちょっと可愛かったな\nなるほど、こういう感じでやればいいのか",
      "startTime": 155.3712145805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "はい。……はい。ええ。分かりました\n……ダメだ、僕じゃあ君みたいに可愛く出来ないな",
      "startTime": 164.4712237357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺は別に可愛くもなんともないし\n真似しても、あまりいいことはないと思うぞ……",
      "startTime": 172.8999763485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "撮影の本番までは、もう少しあるけど\nどうやったら演技が上達するのかなあ",
      "startTime": 179.9734688122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "いや……演技力の問題って訳でもないか\n少しでも、このヒロインの気持ちを理解しないと……",
      "startTime": 188.4068163871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（すぐにうまくいく訳はないと思ってたけど）\n（ここまでとなると、一体どうしたものかな……）",
      "startTime": 196.4333310441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、もうこんなに経ってたんだ\n悪いね、遅くまで手伝わせて",
      "startTime": 204.5546611468,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8778.694057400004,
          "startTime": 213.3333552042
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや。俺こそ、夜にしか付き合えなくて悪いな\nこんな時間だし、寮まで送るよ",
      "startTime": 211.266678619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、夕ご飯をまだ食べてないの？",
      "startTime": 216.0937957446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "夕方の仕事が押して、その後にメールを片付けてたんで\n食べるタイミングを逃してたんだよ……",
      "startTime": 223.6666745499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、葵を送るついでにコンビニで何か見繕うよ",
      "startTime": 226.2114377022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "コンビニだなんて、そんな面倒なことしなくても\n夕飯ぐらい寮で食べていけばいいじゃないか",
      "startTime": 234.3743403118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "寮は星見プロが借りてるんだから\nそこを君が使うのに、なんの遠慮がいるっていうんだ",
      "startTime": 239.9743403118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "みんながいいならだけど……\nそれじゃ、お邪魔させてもらおうかな",
      "startTime": 246.9333412166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ryou_living_yoru"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_02-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、{user}君の分のご飯",
      "startTime": 252.1603577614,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 406.33789689999844,
          "startTime": 252.5666956583
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
